        <p class="ccr009-eyebrow">CCR009 preparation guide</p>
        <h1>How to Prepare for a CCR009 Return</h1>
        <p class="ccr009-hero__lead">Preparing for a CCR009 return is much easier when information is organised throughout the year rather than gathered at the last minute.</p>
        <p class="ccr009-hero__lead">Many FCA-authorised motor dealers search for how to prepare for a CCR009 return shortly before an FCA reporting deadline. By that stage, important information may be stored across multiple systems, making the process more time-consuming than necessary.</p>
        <p class="ccr009-hero__lead">Starting preparation early can make the reporting process significantly easier, reduce the risk of avoidable errors and help ensure information is available when the FCA reporting window opens.</p>
        <p class="ccr009-hero__lead">This guide explains how motor dealers can prepare for a CCR009 return and avoid common reporting problems.</p>
        <div class="ccr009-actions">
          <a class="ccr009-btn ccr009-btn--primary" href="/contact#send-message">Start a CCR009 Enquiry</a>
          <a class="ccr009-btn ccr009-btn--secondary" href="/ccr009-return-assistance-motor-dealers">View CCR009 Return Assistance</a>
        </div>
      </div>
